snippet.title: Unlighted  - Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
In this new update, you may enter into a strange world plenty of objects that are about to be forgotten. Escape from there before it's too late. You still have something that attach you to the real world, so don't lose that. 

Use all the tools at hand, modify gravity to access inaccessible places and reach the shiny threshold in order to survive. Staying within the Umbral Dimension for too long can have severe consequences.
